  "subject": "Drop use of maven versions plugin",
  "commit_message": "Drop use of maven versions plugin\n\nPortal manages its version numbers in its POM files,\nnot using version.properties. Change templates to\nstop invoking the versions:set plugin.\n\nIssue: PORTAL-134\nChange-Id: I8d36e788f24046eca045da534e206bc4034c11f8\nSigned-off-by: Christopher Lott (cl778h) <clott@research.att.com>\n",
